Hi. This is a paid content. We do not unblock it.
For user filter:
```
theathletic.com#$#body { overflow: auto !important; position: unset !important; }
theathletic.com#$##darken-overlay { display: none !important; }
theathletic.com#$##slideup-paywall { display: none !important; }
```

